                <head>148. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d148fn1">Source: Carter Library, Plains File,
                        Box 10. Secret. The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room.
                            <persName corresp="#p_CJ_1">Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig, C” in the
                        upper right corner.</note>
